ActFirst Nations Fiscal Management Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Schedule to the First Nations Fiscal Management Act
PrecisOrder Amending the SCHEDULE TO THE FIRST NATIONS FISCAL MANAGEMENT ACT in order to add the following nine First Nations: Bande des Innus de Pessamit (Quebec); M’Chigeeng First Nation (Ontario); Berens River (Manitoba); Muskowekwan (Saskatchewan); Ehattesaht, Nak’azdli, Seton Lake and Stellat’en First Nation (British Columbia); and Behdzi Ahda” First Nation (Northwest Territories).
